1
00:00:08,221 --> 00:00:10,641
My dear fiancée.

2
00:00:11,091 --> 00:00:12,911
How are you?

3
00:00:14,551 --> 00:00:17,841
It's been a little over a month 
since my life here at the

4
00:00:17,841 --> 00:00:20,121
magic capital of Dirashik started.

5
00:00:21,561 --> 00:00:24,481
I've finally gotten used to school life.

6
00:00:30,961 --> 00:00:33,111
I've made a female friend too.

7
00:00:34,691 --> 00:00:39,241
To gain experience and become a 
gentleman who is worthy of you

8
00:00:39,241 --> 00:00:41,151
I work hard every day.

9
00:00:48,471 --> 00:00:49,571
Kunon.

10
00:00:53,371 --> 00:00:54,761
Nice to meet you.

11
00:00:54,761 --> 00:00:57,461
I'm Elia Hesson of Ability.

12
00:00:57,461 --> 00:00:59,791
Can I interest you in our faction?

13
00:00:59,791 --> 00:01:01,431
Why don't you join us?

14
00:01:03,581 --> 00:01:06,251
Wow she's sparkly and pretty and cute.

15
00:01:06,251 --> 00:01:09,961
I've never seen anyone like her
in the countryside where I'm from.

16
00:01:09,961 --> 00:01:12,071
My heart is starting to race.

17
00:01:13,101 --> 00:01:15,881
I'm more interested in 
you than the faction.

18
00:01:15,881 --> 00:01:18,701
Would that be an impure reason to join?

19
00:01:18,701 --> 00:01:21,451
Great thank you.

20
00:01:21,931 --> 00:01:27,081
People at school often tell me that 
my idea of a gentleman is wrong.

21
00:01:27,601 --> 00:01:29,471
What do you think Your Highness?

22
00:03:01,151 --> 00:03:06,241
FAIRIES CHECKING THE ANSWER

23
00:03:05,281 --> 00:03:06,351
Conflict?

24
00:03:06,841 --> 00:03:10,061
Right. Ability Rationality and Harmony.

25
00:03:10,061 --> 00:03:14,911
These three factions used 
to be in conflict.

26
00:03:14,911 --> 00:03:16,441
Oh yeah?

27
00:03:16,441 --> 00:03:18,861
Hey do you think you can fly higher?

28
00:03:18,861 --> 00:03:20,051
S-Sure.

29
00:03:23,921 --> 00:03:26,451
Yes let's keep you there.

30
00:03:31,741 --> 00:03:35,581
They still get heated up 
when it comes to magic

31
00:03:35,861 --> 00:03:38,591
but it seems they settled down 
into more of a friendly rivalry.

32
00:03:39,561 --> 00:03:41,891
I'm glad this is a peaceful time.

33
00:03:42,221 --> 00:03:47,071
Recently I'm having a lot of fun 
doing experiments with you Kunon.

34
00:03:47,071 --> 00:03:48,371
Kunon Gurion.

35
00:03:53,331 --> 00:03:55,201
She's gorgeous.

36
00:03:55,201 --> 00:03:58,471
The girl from Ability 
was also very cute though.

37
00:03:58,791 --> 00:04:02,561
I'm Elva Daglight from Harmony.

38
00:04:02,561 --> 00:04:07,711
Would you like... to join us?

39
00:04:08,111 --> 00:04:12,251
A lady who shines seductively 
like polished obsidian.

40
00:04:12,681 --> 00:04:17,631
I think she's still a teenager but 
her glamour is making me dizzy.

41
00:04:18,641 --> 00:04:20,621
Why ask such a silly question?

42
00:04:20,621 --> 00:04:24,221
Princess of the moonlight 
everything shall be as you wish.

43
00:04:24,221 --> 00:04:25,261
What?!

44
00:04:25,501 --> 00:04:26,781
It's a promise.

45
00:04:32,491 --> 00:04:34,071
Your magical power is wavering.

46
00:04:34,071 --> 00:04:37,901
If you want to fly long distances 
you need to learn to keep it stable.

47
00:04:37,901 --> 00:04:39,501
Oh sorry.

48
00:04:39,501 --> 00:04:42,781
But Kunon! She was from Harmony!

49
00:04:43,011 --> 00:04:44,251
What of it?

50
00:04:45,071 --> 00:04:47,091
W-Wouldn't that be two-timing?!

51
00:04:47,091 --> 00:04:49,411
Kunon dear!

52
00:04:53,411 --> 00:04:55,661
She's super cute!

53
00:04:57,891 --> 00:04:59,671
Who the hell is he?

54
00:05:00,191 --> 00:05:03,071
I'm Cassis of Rationality.

55
00:05:03,071 --> 00:05:05,551
Will you join us please?!

56
00:05:05,551 --> 00:05:08,181
An exceptionally pretty 
girl's exceptional smile!

57
00:05:09,431 --> 00:05:11,351
I'm glad I came to the city.

58
00:05:11,351 --> 00:05:14,311
Father Mother thank you!

59
00:05:14,311 --> 00:05:16,941
What is up with this guy?

60
00:05:16,941 --> 00:05:18,941
Please Kunon?

61
00:05:18,941 --> 00:05:21,921
You're starting to wobble 
a lot out of nowhere.

62
00:05:21,921 --> 00:05:23,641
You have to focus.

63
00:05:23,641 --> 00:05:24,691
Huh?

64
00:05:26,391 --> 00:05:29,821
L-Listen Kunon. Would you like 
to join Rationality?

65
00:05:29,821 --> 00:05:31,331
Huh? Why would I?

66
00:05:31,331 --> 00:05:31,901
What?

67
00:05:31,901 --> 00:05:32,491
What?

68
00:05:33,081 --> 00:05:35,391
Riyah why don't we finish up?

69
00:05:37,591 --> 00:05:39,431
Huh? Whoa!

70
00:05:39,841 --> 00:05:42,571
H-Hold on Kunon!

71
00:05:47,741 --> 00:05:49,481
This wasn't like you.

72
00:05:49,481 --> 00:05:54,101
Of course two-timing isn't commendable 
and three-timing is even worse

73
00:05:54,101 --> 00:05:55,491
but a request from such a cute—

74
00:05:55,491 --> 00:05:57,571
I would've agreed if a lady had asked.

75
00:05:57,571 --> 00:05:59,511
What?! Then...?

76
00:06:00,401 --> 00:06:02,711
I thought that was the 
cutest of the three.

77
00:06:03,341 --> 00:06:05,331
The city sure is something else.

78
00:06:06,061 --> 00:06:07,241
Kunon.

79
00:06:07,241 --> 00:06:09,761
Ah the sleeping beauty 
from the other day.

80
00:06:09,761 --> 00:06:11,661
H-Hello miss.

81
00:06:11,661 --> 00:06:15,881
Hello. Riyah I heard you're 
joining Rationality.

82
00:06:15,881 --> 00:06:17,651
It's good to have you.

83
00:06:17,651 --> 00:06:19,161
Kunon would you like to join?

84
00:06:19,161 --> 00:06:20,441
Of course!

85
00:06:20,441 --> 00:06:23,771
No gentleman would decline 
an invitation from a lady.

86
00:06:23,771 --> 00:06:27,851
If there is one I'd do a 
double take at his face.

87
00:06:27,851 --> 00:06:29,071
Although I couldn't see it!

88
00:06:30,801 --> 00:06:32,801
He agreed to join three factions?!

89
00:06:33,281 --> 00:06:34,291
Yes.

90
00:06:34,291 --> 00:06:37,631
They will not be happy if they find out!

91
00:06:37,631 --> 00:06:41,811
Right. Even if things are peaceful now
 he can't do that can he?

92
00:06:46,751 --> 00:06:48,321
Cheers!

93
00:06:52,431 --> 00:06:53,771
You did it Elia!

94
00:06:53,771 --> 00:06:56,321
As expected of the biggest 
boy magnet of the faction.

95
00:06:56,321 --> 00:06:58,331
A pretty girl even the goddess 
of beauty would stare at!

96
00:06:58,561 --> 00:07:00,851
Please stop that Mr. Bael.

97
00:07:00,851 --> 00:07:01,991
Nice going pretty girl!

98
00:07:01,991 --> 00:07:04,241
Even though a pretty girl with 
a pure heart is fictional!

99
00:07:04,241 --> 00:07:05,721
Go out with me pretty girl!

100
00:07:05,721 --> 00:07:07,271
No go out with me!

101
00:07:07,271 --> 00:07:09,801
You can cuss me out 
and dump me on the first date!

102
00:07:09,801 --> 00:07:11,471
I'd like to ask your hand for marriage!

103
00:07:11,471 --> 00:07:13,591
Let's pay back a debt of 
500 million necca together!

104
00:07:15,031 --> 00:07:16,811
Celebrate more.

105
00:07:16,811 --> 00:07:21,501
You've managed the difficult task 
of securing a promising newcomer.

106
00:07:21,501 --> 00:07:22,981
Mr. Bael!

107
00:07:22,981 --> 00:07:25,581
Excuse me. I worked hard too.

108
00:07:25,581 --> 00:07:28,361
Yeah good job! You did well too.

109
00:07:28,621 --> 00:07:29,861
Thank you very much—

110
00:07:29,861 --> 00:07:33,481
Now Ability is in stable condition.

111
00:07:34,721 --> 00:07:39,031
Please don't show up out 
of nowhere Mr. Genevis.

112
00:07:39,031 --> 00:07:40,461
I'm sorry.

113
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:42,861
Great work.

114
00:07:44,121 --> 00:07:48,461
He's actually a good guy but the way
 he talks is kind of annoying.

115
00:07:48,461 --> 00:07:50,031
You did it.

116
00:07:50,911 --> 00:07:52,541
Yeah. Cheers!

117
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:58,441
However... there's an unsettling rumor.

118
00:07:59,851 --> 00:08:00,771
A rumor?

119
00:08:01,231 --> 00:08:03,271
Damn you Ability!

120
00:08:05,271 --> 00:08:09,101
Well if it isn't Rationality.

121
00:08:09,901 --> 00:08:12,961
I wish you didn't barge 
in without permission.

122
00:08:13,631 --> 00:08:17,101
As always the way you talk 
pisses me off Genevis!

123
00:08:17,101 --> 00:08:18,401
I'm gonna kick your ass!

124
00:08:19,071 --> 00:08:23,561
Ms. Sandra is as scary as usual.

125
00:08:24,381 --> 00:08:26,801
So full of energy.

126
00:08:26,801 --> 00:08:28,561
Is that because you had meat?

127
00:08:28,561 --> 00:08:30,961
Huh?! Are you picking fight with me?!

128
00:08:30,961 --> 00:08:35,851
He's not really a bad 
person. Just annoying.

129
00:08:36,211 --> 00:08:37,971
Did you need something Lulu?

130
00:08:37,971 --> 00:08:39,651
Yes actually—

131
00:08:39,651 --> 00:08:41,221
Like hell he needs something!

132
00:08:41,651 --> 00:08:44,791
That uggo over there is spreading 
bullshit that she succeeded

133
00:08:44,791 --> 00:08:47,341
in recruiting Kunon 
so we came to complain!

134
00:08:47,341 --> 00:08:49,881
What?! It's not bullshit!

135
00:08:49,881 --> 00:08:51,361
And I'm not ugly!

136
00:08:51,361 --> 00:08:52,671
Shut up ugly!

137
00:08:52,671 --> 00:08:54,461
Everyone is ugly except for me!

138
00:08:54,461 --> 00:08:56,861
Learn to align your attitude 
with your ugly mug!

139
00:08:56,861 --> 00:08:57,861
Excuse me?!

140
00:08:57,861 --> 00:08:59,571
Elia is a sweet girl!

141
00:08:59,571 --> 00:09:02,111
That's right! A sweet girl in love!

142
00:09:02,111 --> 00:09:04,371
I-I'm not in love.

143
00:09:04,371 --> 00:09:06,561
Sweet? Oh please! More like stinky feet—

144
00:09:06,561 --> 00:09:08,181
Cassis stop talking.

145
00:09:08,181 --> 00:09:10,061
Or I can't speak.

146
00:09:11,361 --> 00:09:13,781
Please excuse him Elia.

147
00:09:13,781 --> 00:09:16,131
He likes to tell the truth.

148
00:09:16,391 --> 00:09:18,141
Oh right.

149
00:09:18,141 --> 00:09:20,491
Hm? That's not an apology is it?

150
00:09:20,891 --> 00:09:23,931
And what did you come here for?

151
00:09:23,931 --> 00:09:27,021
We determined the order of 
recruitment fair and square.

152
00:09:27,301 --> 00:09:32,901
Yes. But there is an unsettling rumor 
so we came to check the answer.

153
00:09:32,901 --> 00:09:34,301
A rumor?

154
00:09:35,871 --> 00:09:38,841
Shilto should be heading here right now.

155
00:09:38,841 --> 00:09:40,281
I am here.

156
00:09:50,061 --> 00:09:55,051
As we agreed we approached 
Kunon Gurion in the order of

157
00:09:55,361 --> 00:09:58,051
Ability Harmony and Rationality.

158
00:09:58,051 --> 00:10:00,161
Yes and that's why we—

159
00:10:00,161 --> 00:10:03,231
He said yes to all three factions.

160
00:10:03,231 --> 00:10:04,141
What?!

161
00:10:04,931 --> 00:10:09,851
Technically Ability 
failed the initial approach

162
00:10:09,851 --> 00:10:12,751
but the second student succeeded.

163
00:10:12,751 --> 00:10:13,271
I did.

164
00:10:13,271 --> 00:10:14,271
Ugh!

165
00:10:14,821 --> 00:10:18,571
Why not me?

166
00:10:18,921 --> 00:10:20,761
This is unprecedented.

167
00:10:21,131 --> 00:10:24,831
It seems... we've got someone 
truly out of the box.

168
00:10:24,831 --> 00:10:29,641
Is he serious or is it all lies?

169
00:10:29,641 --> 00:10:32,211
We'll just have to ask him directly.

170
00:10:58,031 --> 00:10:59,331
The master of the forest!

171
00:10:59,331 --> 00:11:00,821
Let's run Princess Mirika!

172
00:11:01,601 --> 00:11:02,821
No we can't.

173
00:11:06,671 --> 00:11:08,691
There's a village up ahead.

174
00:11:08,691 --> 00:11:11,501
So I have to stop it right here!

175
00:11:39,821 --> 00:11:40,961
Dear brother!

176
00:11:40,961 --> 00:11:43,071
Prince Lyle!

177
00:11:44,951 --> 00:11:46,331
You've got guts.

178
00:11:46,641 --> 00:11:49,451
That's what I expect from the 
vice captain of the Wild Bears.

179
00:11:49,751 --> 00:11:50,951
Not at all.

180
00:11:52,541 --> 00:11:53,931
I still have much to learn.

181
00:12:04,471 --> 00:12:06,721
Coming back after the sun has set?

182
00:12:07,021 --> 00:12:09,241
Where does she go out to?

183
00:12:11,431 --> 00:12:13,601
Welcome back Princess Mirika.

184
00:12:13,601 --> 00:12:14,981
I'm home Laura.

185
00:12:15,471 --> 00:12:19,921
You received a missive from the senior 
school for nobles about the final exam.

186
00:12:21,751 --> 00:12:22,881
The time has come.

187
00:12:22,881 --> 00:12:26,241
And another letter.

188
00:12:29,001 --> 00:12:30,411
From Kunon?!

189
00:12:49,821 --> 00:12:53,871
"My dear fiancée." Oh my!

190
00:12:55,151 --> 00:12:57,811
So he's doing a lot of magic experiments.

191
00:13:00,251 --> 00:13:02,151
A bacon-making experiment?

192
00:13:02,381 --> 00:13:06,061
I see you still like bacon Kunon.

193
00:13:06,061 --> 00:13:06,791
Huh?!

194
00:13:07,981 --> 00:13:09,161
Is everything okay?

195
00:13:11,281 --> 00:13:14,161
He's made a female friend.

196
00:13:16,001 --> 00:13:18,921
She must be his classmate. 
Nothing to worry about.

197
00:13:20,361 --> 00:13:24,421
R-Right nothing to worry about.

198
00:13:25,911 --> 00:13:29,051
Isn't that right Kunon?

199
00:13:37,891 --> 00:13:39,901
I'd like to start a 
household account book.

200
00:13:40,121 --> 00:13:41,411
What is that?

201
00:13:41,411 --> 00:13:45,151
And why do you need my shopping memos?

202
00:13:45,151 --> 00:13:48,211
Keeping precise records 
of income and expenses

203
00:13:48,211 --> 00:13:51,501
is the most important 
thing in making money.

204
00:13:51,501 --> 00:13:54,151
What do you do with the 
money you make at school?

205
00:13:54,151 --> 00:13:56,031
I chuck it into the drawer.

206
00:13:56,031 --> 00:13:57,481
And the receipts?

207
00:13:57,481 --> 00:14:00,921
You've bought stuff like seeds of 
whatever and lots of meat haven't you?

208
00:14:01,271 --> 00:14:07,201
I don't have the receipts but I 
wrote down all income and expenses.

209
00:14:07,201 --> 00:14:09,651
It's part of a noble's education.

210
00:14:09,651 --> 00:14:11,721
I was told to keep good records.

211
00:14:11,721 --> 00:14:13,891
That makes it easier!

212
00:14:13,891 --> 00:14:15,191
Please give me those memos.

213
00:14:15,191 --> 00:14:15,911
What?

214
00:14:16,641 --> 00:14:19,411
Hmm where did they go?

215
00:14:19,411 --> 00:14:22,261
I piled stuff up too high in
 my lab and it all fell down

216
00:14:22,261 --> 00:14:23,351
so I haven't touched it since.

217
00:14:23,351 --> 00:14:24,611
Master Kunon!

218
00:14:24,611 --> 00:14:26,111
Wow scary!

219
00:14:26,111 --> 00:14:28,611
Go through it and find them all please!

220
00:14:28,611 --> 00:14:31,111
R-Really?

221
00:14:31,971 --> 00:14:35,621
I'm not good at organizing 
and keeping things tidy.

222
00:14:37,131 --> 00:14:41,121
Master Kunon! You'll be late for school.

223
00:14:41,121 --> 00:14:42,501
Coming!

224
00:14:47,741 --> 00:14:49,381
Good morning Kunon.

225
00:14:49,821 --> 00:14:51,381
Good morning.

226
00:14:51,661 --> 00:14:53,761
Good morning Kunon.

227
00:14:53,761 --> 00:14:55,791
Good morning.

228
00:14:55,791 --> 00:14:58,371
Your voice is as beautiful as ever.

229
00:14:58,371 --> 00:15:02,651
It's as if I can also hear the beautiful 
voice in your beautiful heart.

230
00:15:13,041 --> 00:15:14,661
Good morning.

231
00:15:14,991 --> 00:15:17,181
Good morning Miss Reyes.

232
00:15:19,021 --> 00:15:20,331
That bacon...

233
00:15:20,331 --> 00:15:22,001
Hide yourself now!

234
00:15:22,001 --> 00:15:23,671
Hank that bacon!

235
00:15:23,671 --> 00:15:26,811
I came up with the idea last night 
and made it first thing this morning.

236
00:15:26,811 --> 00:15:27,571
But whatever!

237
00:15:27,571 --> 00:15:29,661
Now's not the time for that!

238
00:15:29,661 --> 00:15:32,481
The seniors from the factions 
are looking for you.

239
00:15:32,481 --> 00:15:33,261
Me?

240
00:15:33,261 --> 00:15:37,181
You saying yes to all the factions 
has become a huge problem.

241
00:15:37,181 --> 00:15:38,701
If they find you who knows what—

242
00:15:38,701 --> 00:15:40,021
I found you!

243
00:15:42,051 --> 00:15:45,801
Come with me. 
The representative is waiting.

244
00:15:48,311 --> 00:15:52,031
Nice to meet you
 one who is passionate like the sun.

245
00:15:52,031 --> 00:15:53,961
I'm happy to follow you anywhere.

246
00:15:53,961 --> 00:15:55,821
Wait are you mad?

247
00:15:55,821 --> 00:15:57,331
A little.

248
00:15:57,331 --> 00:15:59,581
If it's only a little then no big deal.

249
00:16:01,431 --> 00:16:02,831
Thank you for the food.

250
00:16:04,701 --> 00:16:06,691
Mmm tasty!

251
00:16:06,691 --> 00:16:09,251
This is Hank's new bacon sandwich.

252
00:16:09,251 --> 00:16:10,961
Would you like some ladies?

253
00:16:11,671 --> 00:16:13,531
No thank you.

254
00:16:13,531 --> 00:16:14,971
Finish it already.

255
00:16:15,451 --> 00:16:19,221
How can he be so calm in this situation?

256
00:16:19,871 --> 00:16:23,191
Today's smoked fish isn't too bad.

257
00:16:23,821 --> 00:16:27,311
It doesn't make me nauseous 
and it's just salty enough.

258
00:16:27,311 --> 00:16:31,271
Perhaps you should consider 
smoking fish more often?

259
00:16:31,271 --> 00:16:33,111
Business as usual over here too.

260
00:16:33,111 --> 00:16:35,301
Fish is tasty as well

261
00:16:35,301 --> 00:16:40,411
but the ocean is far from here 
so we don't get fresh fish often.

262
00:16:40,771 --> 00:16:43,421
Apparently sorcerers 
who have traveled far

263
00:16:43,421 --> 00:16:46,541
sometimes bring back frozen seafood 
to make some pocket money.

264
00:16:46,541 --> 00:16:49,621
Those are the only times you 
can get fish around here.

265
00:16:49,621 --> 00:16:52,131
Is that so? How unfortunate.

266
00:16:52,371 --> 00:16:56,381
But do you think freshwater 
fish can be farmed near here?

267
00:16:56,661 --> 00:16:58,131
I wonder.

268
00:16:58,131 --> 00:17:00,531
Maybe look for research 
reports at the library?

269
00:17:00,531 --> 00:17:06,451
Kunon if I find the reports and it seems 
it could be done would you help me?

270
00:17:04,451 --> 00:17:06,831
Never mind that. Please go now.

271
00:17:06,831 --> 00:17:08,331
It'd be my pleasure!

272
00:17:09,021 --> 00:17:15,531
How lucky am I to be 
escorted by so many fairies?

273
00:17:17,341 --> 00:17:18,491
Kunon.

274
00:17:18,491 --> 00:17:20,931
W-Will he be okay?

275
00:17:20,931 --> 00:17:23,781
Granted I don't see how 
he could be though.

276
00:17:23,781 --> 00:17:26,031
Did you see fairies somewhere?

277
00:17:26,031 --> 00:17:28,921
Oh... That was a metaphor.

278
00:17:33,381 --> 00:17:35,241
This is incredible.

279
00:17:35,581 --> 00:17:38,351
I didn't know there was a castle
 like this on the school grounds.

280
00:17:38,351 --> 00:17:39,911
Shut up and walk.

281
00:17:39,911 --> 00:17:46,171
If you'll escort me I'll stay 
quiet and follow you anywhere.

282
00:17:47,001 --> 00:17:48,791
Then talk more.

283
00:17:50,761 --> 00:17:52,651
He's here representative!

284
00:17:57,191 --> 00:18:02,161
Welcome. I am Bael Kirkington 
representative of Ability

285
00:18:02,161 --> 00:18:03,911
and we use this castle as a base.

286
00:18:04,281 --> 00:18:07,241
Nice to meet you. I'm Kunon Gurion.

287
00:18:07,971 --> 00:18:10,421
So these are representatives.

288
00:18:10,701 --> 00:18:12,321
First let me apologize.

289
00:18:12,321 --> 00:18:16,091
I'm sorry for summoning you like this 
when you don't belong to any faction yet.

290
00:18:16,671 --> 00:18:20,931
I'm honored to have been invited. 
Thank you for having me.

291
00:18:21,721 --> 00:18:27,181
I think it's some massive creature
 but it's too big to really tell.

292
00:18:27,641 --> 00:18:30,671
But I trust you know 
why you were summoned?

293
00:18:30,991 --> 00:18:35,071
My name is Lulomet and I'm the 
representative of Rationality.

294
00:18:35,391 --> 00:18:36,591
Nice to meet you.

295
00:18:36,971 --> 00:18:39,371
A dark tree like a shadow.

296
00:18:39,371 --> 00:18:42,571
First time seeing a person with a plant.

297
00:18:42,791 --> 00:18:45,831
I'm the representative of Harmony Shilto.

298
00:18:50,841 --> 00:18:52,251
Nice to meet you.

299
00:18:52,251 --> 00:18:54,171
I've been wanting to meet you.

300
00:18:54,171 --> 00:18:57,341
I hope you can make time to spend with me.

301
00:18:57,341 --> 00:18:58,241
What?

302
00:18:58,241 --> 00:18:59,001
Huh?

303
00:19:03,341 --> 00:19:04,721
Hey brat!

304
00:19:04,721 --> 00:19:07,241
Do you realize the situation you're in?!

305
00:19:07,241 --> 00:19:09,531
This is your fault!

306
00:19:08,231 --> 00:19:09,531
Sandra.

307
00:19:09,531 --> 00:19:12,351
Because of you three factions 
are about to get into a fight.

308
00:19:12,351 --> 00:19:13,731
How are you going to settle this?!

309
00:19:13,951 --> 00:19:16,231
Please don't fight over me.

310
00:19:17,391 --> 00:19:18,671
Fish.

311
00:19:19,111 --> 00:19:20,741
Water attribute?

312
00:19:20,741 --> 00:19:22,901
I have a feeling we'll get along.

313
00:19:22,901 --> 00:19:25,801
I'm sure the magic you use is wonderful.

314
00:19:25,801 --> 00:19:26,971
Do you have time after this?

315
00:19:26,971 --> 00:19:29,001
Would you like to talk about magic?

316
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:32,001
He's... crazy.

317
00:19:33,481 --> 00:19:35,901
He indulges women and 
is weak against women.

318
00:19:35,901 --> 00:19:39,161
It's just as the report said...
No it's more than that.

319
00:19:39,591 --> 00:19:43,901
It seems it'll be faster 
to speak to him via Shilto.

320
00:19:43,901 --> 00:19:45,041
Me?

321
00:19:47,151 --> 00:19:52,231
Questioned by you I may tell 
more than you ask.

322
00:19:52,231 --> 00:19:54,021
How about we do this over some tea?

323
00:19:57,521 --> 00:20:01,561
Let's do that. This might take a while.

324
00:20:01,561 --> 00:20:02,541
Right.

325
00:20:08,571 --> 00:20:12,451
Nice to meet you. I am Genevis.

326
00:20:12,451 --> 00:20:16,441
Please feel free to call 
me Geneva with affection.

327
00:20:18,801 --> 00:20:22,421
N-Nice to meet you Mr. Geneva.

328
00:20:23,031 --> 00:20:25,931
An evil spirit. No a human?

329
00:20:26,691 --> 00:20:28,491
What's wrong?

330
00:20:28,491 --> 00:20:31,391
Could it be my laughter?

331
00:20:31,741 --> 00:20:36,301
Sorry. I just can't help it.

332
00:20:52,481 --> 00:20:56,211
So which faction will you 
choose at the end of the day?

333
00:21:03,111 --> 00:21:07,261
Earlier... That was scarier than Rinko.

334
00:21:14,801 --> 00:21:17,101
Which faction do you want to join?

335
00:21:17,101 --> 00:21:19,111
Yours of course!

336
00:21:19,581 --> 00:21:21,731
That's what I wish I could say.

337
00:21:23,691 --> 00:21:24,611
Which one?

338
00:21:25,011 --> 00:21:27,921
Many ladies have recruited me

339
00:21:27,921 --> 00:21:32,011
but it's impossible for 
me to choose just one.

340
00:21:32,011 --> 00:21:32,871
Therefore...

341
00:21:38,121 --> 00:21:40,751
I'm going to join all factions.

342
00:21:40,751 --> 00:21:41,631
Huh?

343
00:21:41,861 --> 00:21:42,501
What?

344
00:23:35,911 --> 00:23:39,371
Next episode:
 "The Unprecedented Troublemaker."

345
00:23:36,251 --> 00:23:40,001
NEXT TIME: THE UNPRECEDENTED TROUBLEMAKER
